<sect2>
<title>Installation de <application>KOffice</application></title>

<para>Installez <application>KOffice</application> en lançant les commandes
suivantes:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>export QTDIR=/opt/qt 
./configure --prefix=&kde-dir; --disable-debug &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>
